summary: 2010 COACH HOUSE MOTORHOME.  CONSUMER WRITES IN REGARDS TO TIRE MONITORING SYSTEM ISSUES.  CONSUMER HAS DIFFERENT VEHICLE COMPLAINT LISTED IN ARTEMIS.  *SMD  THE CONSUMER EXPERIENCED A TIRE BLOWOUT, ON THE RIGHT REAR PASSENGER INNER TIRE.
